      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI reported for hemolysis index QoI on at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed; observed order of accuracy near 1.8 for velocity but hemolysis index GCI exceeds 5% on finest mesh pair. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
    },
    {
