      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation (hemolysis index, shear stress) are directly mapped to clinical decision thresholds with documented traceability.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is directly relevant; however, traceability documentation linking predicted QoIs to specific clinical thresholds is incomplete. Achieved level 3 is below required level 4."
