      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on device geometry and operating conditions representative of clinical VAD use envelope.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry at nominal operating point only; clinical VAD operating envelope spans broader speed and flow ranges not covered. Achieved level 2 is well below required level 4."
