      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between CFD boundary condition parameters and experimentally measured inlet/outlet conditions demonstrated quantitatively for all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Equivalency mapping was partially documented for flow rate and rotational speed; pressure boundary equivalency was not demonstrated for the high-speed operating point."
